## API base URL

Default production API: `https://doughnut.odd-e.com`. **`pnpm cli`** sets `DOUGHNUT_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:9081` and `DOUGHNUT_CONFIG_DIR=~/.config/doughnut-dev`. Production-style: `pnpm cli -P` / `--production`. Self-hosted: set `DOUGHNUT_API_BASE_URL`.

**Recall load delay (tests/manual):** `DOUGHNUT_CLI_SLOW_RECALL_LOAD_MS` ‚Äî see `cli/src/recall.ts`.

## OAuth credentials (Gmail)

Build-time injection. Local: `cli/.env.local` from `cli/.env.local.example`. CI: `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` / `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` secrets.

## Adding new commands

Ensure `/help` lists the command:

1. Export **CommandDoc** from the handler module (`category`: `subcommand` | `interactive`).
2. Register in **`help.ts`** (`subcommandDocs`, module doc arrays, or `interactiveDocs`).
3. Wire **`processInput()`** (interactive) or **`index.ts`** (subcommand).
4. Verify with `pnpm cli` ‚Üí `/help` or `pnpm cli -c "/help"`.
